00:36:05.905 --> 00:36:08.145
that implies that certain views are acceptable

684
00:36:08.145 --> 00:36:09.265
and that others are not.

685
00:36:10.045 --> 00:36:11.545
Second, by a growing sense,

686
00:36:11.545 --> 00:36:13.985
